HEADWORD: Encoubert
<hw>En`cou`bert"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., Pg.
<ets>encorberto</ets>, <ets>encuberto</ets>, lit., covered.]</ety>
<fld>(Zo⟦oum⟧l.)</fld> <def>One of several species of armadillos of the
